{"word":"G1709 - ἐμπνέω - empnéō - emp-neh'-o - Breathe","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐμπνέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">empnéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">emp-neh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Breathe</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சீறு"},{"paragraph":"1. to breathe in or on"},{"paragraph":"2. to inhale"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1722 - ἐν - en - en/1722\">G1722</a> and <a href=\"#/G4154 - πνέω - pnéō - pneh'-o/4154\">G4154</a>; to <i>inhale</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>be animated by</i> (<i>bent upon</i>): - breathe.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}